          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM &amp; TV CREW">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM COLLINS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>Int. deon'S APARTMENT BUILDING</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They walk down the hallway to the front door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="782">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>3 lock’s? Bet your rent’s cheap.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="783">DeoN</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I like things to be the same when I get home.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Deon opens the door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="102" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="78" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DR. CARTER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE, DEON &amp; RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PETE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM &amp; TV CREW">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM COLLINS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. lIVING ROOM - nIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="784">Ron</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We made it, yes! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="785">Deon</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Never been so glad to be home.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="786">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It’s so nice to be inside even this crappy place looks good.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ron closes the front window and peep’s outside as Keke and Deon sit at the table. On the TV is WNG’s Tom Collins.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="787">tom Collins</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Violent outbreaks were just happening in the black and Latino areas of the city. Now there are reports of increase violence all over the state. It’s believed Edibl Eats popularity expanded way pass the inner-city.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Tom looks as if hearing something being said to him.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ToM COLLINS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We have breaking news to report. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>A picture of MARK on screen over Tom’s shoulder. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Tom cOLLINS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>MARK, the CEO of Edibl Eats has been found dead from what authorities are saying is suicide. His company was under intense investigation and authorities believe the fear of going to prison is the reason he committed suicide.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="788">Keke, Deon &amp; Ron</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Now thats fake news!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>kEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn, I kind of forgot I had this.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Keke takes out a bag of Edibl Eats and puts it on the table. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It’s dumb but part of me still wants to eat it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Shouldn’t, knowing the truth but... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They walk closer to the table looking at the Edibl Eats. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Before we do something crazy... I’m glad you’re here with me.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Deon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Being with you is what got me through this day.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They embrace and kiss. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Suddenly, thats not what I want anymore. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You’re what I need right now. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="103" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 3/8" Page="80" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DR. CARTER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PETE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM &amp; TV CREW">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TOM COLLINS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="1267">doctor office</Text>
      <Text> - nIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Split screen of DR. CARTER and TOM comes on TV screen. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="789">Tom</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Dr. Carter, now that we know what has happen, do you think this is the end of GMDF’s.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="790">dr. CARTER</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I hope not. Research shows that Genetically Modified Designer Foods are very safe to eat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ToM</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How is Edibl Eats different? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Dr. cARTER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The chemicals in Edibl Eats stimulated the part of the brain that brings you joy and comfort... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>TV shows scenes of happy people eating Edibl Eats.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Dr. cARTER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Which feels really good for people living under the constant pressure of stress. But when its cut off, thats a stimulus for anger and frustration... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>TV shows people fighting and destroying property.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ToM COLLINS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That explains whats happening to people right now.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Dr. cARTER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The people who always get harmed the most are the ones who were already struggling to begin with. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Tom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Is there any antidote for this?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Dr. CARTER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Letting the withdraw process run its course. Although reports have come in that when people do something helpful for others, they seem to recover from it quicker. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ToM</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>How is that possible?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Dr. cARTER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I guess the power of love can heal.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>A PATIENT with their arm in a sling and butt exposed runs down a hallway behind Dr. Carter.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="791">Pete</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t need no damn medicine! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s... Pete! He’s alive! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Tom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Dr. Carter. We’ll let you get back to your job as you are needed. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Pete is grabbed and restrained by </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1269">2 HOSPITAL WORKERS</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>PeTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I need some EE’s and red sauce...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>TV cuts to Tom.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Glad you made it Pete.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>tom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>In front of me now could be the last Edibl Eats in the U.S...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The camera zooms in on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1271">the Edibl Eats bag</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>tom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Have to admit, I too had some good times eating this... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Tom takes it out the bag.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This isn’t going to end well.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>tom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Let’s get a close up on this. Now we’ll do the right thing and dispose of this... Wait, guys get back behind the cameras. I didn’t mean like that... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Hands start reaching for the Edibl Eats.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Tom</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wait...Hold on... Back the fuck up!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Tom takes a big bite. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="792">Tom &amp; TV Crew</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Give me some... get back... one last taste... Mmmmm!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>TV go’s black, then a graphic, “We are experiencing Technical Difficulty. Please Stand By.” Deon turns the TV off.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Ron</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>These fools just won’t give up. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Deon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Who!?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Deon and Keke peep out the window and the EE Addicts are all coming into the building.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>RoN (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The whole neighborhood!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="104" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="82" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. dEON'S APARTMENT hallway - nIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ray, Pook, White Lady, Edibl Eats Addicts #1 &amp; 2 are stopping in front of each apartment’s door as Ray takes a deep inhale.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="793">Ray</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea I smell something good!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="794">Pook</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Might be last chance to eat some.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="105" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="82" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. inside OF DEON’S place </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ron looks at the Edibl Eats on the table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="795">roN</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Where’d that come from? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Deon grabs the Edibl Eats and put’s it in the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1170">refrigerator</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="106" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="83" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. dEON'S APARTMENT HALLWAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They are now walking in front of Deon’s door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="796">RAY</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It’s close... Damn, where‘d it go? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="797">Pook</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t lose it!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="107" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="83" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. inside OF DEON’S place</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They’re all smiles but suddenly Ron grabs his stomach. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="798">RoN</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn, I got to fart.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="799">DEON</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Please hold it! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>RoN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m trying to...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="800">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Go to the bathroom!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ron takes two step towards the bathroom but out of his butt comes </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1173">a sound like a trumpet, playing a sustaining </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1174">tooooooot</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Damn, did you eat Miles Davis horn? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="108" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="83" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. dEON'S APARTMENT HALLWay</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="801">raY</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Parenthetical">
      <Text>(sniffing around)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I thought it was here... Wait... </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ray starts sniffing and makes a stink face. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>raY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>...Oh yea, this some Edibl Eats alright. I can smell it through the funk. Coming, from, right, here!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>He point’s to Deon’s door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>raY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Open up. I smell your ass in there! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="802">Pook</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Lets break the door down!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They all begin to bang against the door. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="109" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="84" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. lIVING ROOM</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They run to the door to hold it close. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="110" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="84" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. outside deon’s front door - nIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Pook takes out his gun.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="803">Pook</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Get back, I’m shoot the locks off.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="111" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="84" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>Int. lIVING ROOM</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>They run away from the front door. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="112" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="84" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. ouTSIDE DEON'S FRONT DOOr</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1178">Pook shoots lock #1, lock #2.</Text>
      <Text> Then the gun just clicks.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="804">RaY</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t stop, it’s got another lock.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="805">Pook</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m...I’m out of bullets. Guess I used too many at the other place.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="113" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="84" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>Int. INSIDE OF DEON’S PLACE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The door is being banged hard but still holds. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="806">DEON</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Bet y’all glad I got 3 locks now! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>A loud crash from an apartment below is heard.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="114" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="84" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MAN’S VOICE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. oUTSIDE DEON'S FRONT DOOR</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="807">Man’s voice</Text>
      <Text> (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Give me that Edibl Eats!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The Edibl Eats Addicts begin to run toward another place downstairs. Several gun shots are heard. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="808">Pook</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>We up here and its downstairs? </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="809">raY</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>No its here. My nose ain’t ...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1180">Pook hit’s Ray right in his nose</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Pook</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If you made me miss some I’m find a bullet and shoot yo ass!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Pook runs off as Ray get’s up holding his nose.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>RaY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>My nose.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The door opens and Deon steps out. Ray swings but Deon blocks it and slams Ray against the wall. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="810">DEON</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m done with looking over my back. You still playing a game that is rigged against you! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I ain’t trying to hear that, give me some Edibl Eats! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="811">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That stuff has turned you into a killer. You got to quit!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Quit?! Long as you black you can’t quit. We stuck living in this disaster zone. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And nobody gonna save us but us.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Deon pushes Ray away. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>RAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ain’t nobody bout that BS! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="115" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="85" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. lIVING ROOM - nIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="General">
      <Text>Deon comes back in. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="812">Ron</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I’m going to check on Brandy. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="813">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Tell her thanks.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ron leaves. Deon and Keke sit on the </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1182">couch</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="814">DEON</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ray is right. We do live in a disaster zone. Not caused by a hurricane or earthquake. But from a worse catastrophe. Racism. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The sounds of chaos are heard outside.  </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="116" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="86" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="C">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="COOKING SHOW LADY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="LITTLE BOY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MOTHER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOKIE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. lIVING ROOM - dAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Ron comes in the front door waking up Keke and Deon.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="815">roN</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Y’all gotta see this!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="816">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If it’s people still going crazy, I’d rather look out the window. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ron</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Just come and check this out!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="117" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 7/8" Page="86" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="C">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="LITTLE BOY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MOTHER">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="POOK">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RAY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="RON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>ExT. uRBAN STREET IN FRONT OF DEON’S APARTMENT - dAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Brandy and 2 Social Workers are around the Mother of the Little Boy. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1184">She’s helping him to throw up</Text>
      <Text> the Edibl Eats. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="817">MOTHER</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s it, that’s it...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="818">LITTLE BOY</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t want to momma! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>MoTHER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I know baby but you got to get it out! I did it and now you have too. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>LiTTLE BOY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Please don’t make me...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The Mother sticks her finger down the Little Boy’s throat  causing him to throws up again.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>MoTHER</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s it, get it out. I’m so sorry for feeding you this crap.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>People encourage her. A scream from down the street is heard. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="819">POOK</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Get away from me. This is mine! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Pook has Edibl Eats in one hand and a gun in the other. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="820">ray</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t eat it man. That stuff is poison. It made us go crazy! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>PoOK</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I don’t care, get back!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Please don’t eat it bro. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>pOOK</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>You lucky I got some.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="821">Ron</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>    (Under his breath)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Guest I should of done a better job of getting rid of it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="822">Deon</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>If you eat that, you’ll be doing what they want you to do. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="823">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Fight it, I know you can. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>POOK</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Y’all mad because you ain’t got none. Just get away from me! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>The real you wouldn’t be eating out the garbage. We been setup!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>DEON</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Got us believing that our lives ain’t worth nothing. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>It’s this crap that changed us. Got us killing ourselves for them. And nobody gone save us but us!   </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>He looks at Deon.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Ray</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>I realize that now. We are better than this!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Pook look’s at the Edibl Eats and the look of hunger is replace with the look of anger as he throws it back into the trash can. He then makes himself throw up. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>That’s it brother, get that mess out of you. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>The people around begin to encourage him. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>roN</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Wow, check this out on Social Media. This is happening all over the country. People are reclaiming their minds and bodies. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="118" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="88" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DEON">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="1273">people around a fire and medical van</Text>
      <Text> - dAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Video on his phone shows PEOPLE throwing Edibl Eats into a fire and a Mobile Medical van giving treatment to people. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Ms. Adams was right. The truth will make them want to stop being used. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>Deon</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>And hopefully, never be used again. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Number="119" Type="Scene Heading">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 3/8" Page="88" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ARMORED FIGHTER 1">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="HENRY">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="KEKE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="REPRESENTATIVE DICKENS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="TERRI">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No">
              <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Arial" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style=""></Text>
            </Paragraph>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="1186">fACTORY LOADING DOCK</Text>
      <Text> - nIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1188">Boxes </Text>
      <Text>are being loaded onto </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1190">3 refrigerated trucks</Text>
      <Text>. On one of the boxes </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1192">a label reads, “Edibl Eats Ribs”</Text>
      <Text>. A HAND slaps another label on top saying </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1194">“Juicy’s Ribs”</Text>
      <Text>, then its put on a truck. A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1197">cellphone rings</Text>
      <Text>, hand lifts it up to reveal Henry.   </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="824">HENRY</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yes, being shipped as we speak. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Trucks one and two drive off from the dock. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="825">REPRESENTATIVE DICKENS</Text>
      <Text> (V.O.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Good! Destroy everything. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>HENRY </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Will do sir.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>As he watches the third truck pull away, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1199">the first truck explodes, then second, then the third</Text>
      <Text>, knocking Henry off his feet. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1275">Two ARMORED FIGHTERS </Text>
      <Text>run towards Henry. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1277">Three Private Soldiers</Text>
      <Text> run out the factory and </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1201">start shooting </Text>
      <Text>at them but they are shot down by gunfire from inside the factory. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>RePRESENTATIVE DICKENS (O.S.)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Henry...Henry what happening!?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>As Henry lies on his back, Armored Fighter 1 picks up Henry’s cellphone and looks at Representative Dickens.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="826">Armored fighter 1</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Hello Representative Dickens, good to meet you! Henry can’t make it to the phone right now but we’ll get back with you later, bye.                                                      </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Armored Fighter 1 turns off Henry’s cell. ARMORED FIGHTER 2 looks into a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1204">security camera thats on the dock</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>POV of the security camera looking at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="" TagNumber="1206">Armored Fighter 2, who aims at it and shoots </Text>
      <Text>causing the image to go black. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Armored Fighter 1 looks at Henry on his back looking up at them. Armored Fighter 1 and 2 slides up their face shields and we see that its Keke and Deon. Armored Fighters 3 and 4 join them, their face shields slide up to reveal Ray and Pook. Deon extends a cellphone towards Henry so he can see who is on the screen. </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="827">TERRI</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>People will believe you committed suicide too. Told you that you wasn’t going to get away with it!                         </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>HENRY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Don’t shoot, Reginald’s alive! </Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="0" Background="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Color="#000000000000" Font="Courier Final Draft" RevisionID="0" Size="12" Style="AllCaps" TagNumber="828">KEKE</Text>
      <Text></Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>Yea, we know. This boot should be going up your ass. But for now...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>Her combat boot fills up most of the frame on the screen.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Character">
      <Text>KEKE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue">
      <Text>This will do.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>She kicks, screen goes black, music up.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Action">
      <Text>THE END</Text>
    </Paragraph>
  </Content>

